h1. riakTemplate

h2. Purpose

A Spring bean that provides access to the Spring Data @RiakTemplate@ API

h2. Examples

{code:java}
def riak

def foo = {
  def notifs = riakTemplate.get("notifications", "myuser")
  render "Notifications: $notifs"
}
{code}

h2. Description

See the Spring Data reference for more information on the methods available and on examples of using the @RiakTemplate@ in your own code.